<p>To convert String to Hexadecimal i am using:</p>  <pre><code>public String toHex(String arg) {     return String.format("%040x", new BigInteger(1, arg.getBytes("UTF-8"))); } </code></pre>  <p>This is outlined in the top-voted answer here: <a href="http://stackoverflow.com/questions/923863/converting-a-string-to-hexadecimal-in-java">Converting A String To Hexadecimal In Java</a></p>  <p><em>How do i do the reverse i.e Hexadecimal to String?</em></p>